# Take Screenshot
# Selection
"import ~/Pictures/screenshot.jpg"
  Print
"import ~/Pictures/screenshot.jpg; pinta ~/Pictures/screenshot.jpg"
  Shift + Print
# Full Screen
"import -window root ~/Pictures/screenshot.jpg"
  control + Print
"import -window root ~/Pictures/screenshot.jpg; pinta ~/Pictures/screenshot.jpg"
  control + shift + Print

# Map standby to the standby key (sigh).
